Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:35.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伴随着结尾即开始的咏叹调
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:40.36,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高举白旗的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.88,0:22:46.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在逃狱后的欢呼声中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.12,0:22:50.31,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被强行拷上了手铐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.75,0:22:56.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看吧 愚昧的棋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.19,0:23:01.24,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这定罪的把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:03.97,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇异的独角戏舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:06.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你的眼睛看着 竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.69,0:23:11.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}遗落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:11.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺骗吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:14.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多线并行的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:17.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拨开人群
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.14,0:23:19.85,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呼喊着 这是我正义的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.85,0:23:22.23,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}许下你的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.23,0:23:24.84,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}值得赞美的惊恐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:27.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唯独拒绝丧失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.54,0:23:32.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}指引我吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:35.24,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}过于艳丽的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.29,0:23:37.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}带有偏见的分类
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:39.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要相信没有故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:41.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:43.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我们已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:45.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人人都爱着绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.53,0:23:48.94,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我会满怀悲伤地离去
